sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant REST as OVMS REST Handler<br/>REST port/TCP HTTP
    participant V3 as OpenAI V3 Handler
    participant MM as Model Manager<br/>Watcher + Cleaner Threads
    participant LLM as LLMExecutor<br/>Continuous Batching<br/>Worker Thread
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>CPU/GPU/NPU
    participant GenAI as OpenVINO GenAI<br/>ContinuousBatchingPipeline
    participant S3 as Cloud Storage<br/>S3/GCS/Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 1: REST Inference Request (KServe v2)
    Client->>KRBAC: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform)
    KRBAC->>REST: Forward (HTTP localhost)<br/>No encryption
    REST->>MM: getModel() + infer()
    MM->>OV: ov::InferRequest::infer()
    OV-->>MM: Inference result
    MM-->>REST: Prediction response
    REST-->>KRBAC: JSON response
    KRBAC-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completion (Streaming)
    Client->>REST: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer API key (optional)<br/>stream: true
    REST->>V3: OpenAIChatCompletionsHandler
    V3->>LLM: addRequestToPipeline()<br/>Returns GenerationHandle
    LLM->>GenAI: pipeline.step() [tight loop]
    GenAI->>OV: Token generation
    OV-->>GenAI: Next token
    GenAI-->>LLM: GenerationOutput
    loop SSE Streaming
        LLM-->>V3: Token via GenerationHandle
        V3-->>REST: SSE data chunk
        REST-->>Client: text/event-stream
    end

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 3: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    MM->>MM: Watcher thread detects<br/>config change (MD5)
    MM->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / OAuth2 / Azure MI
    S3-->>MM: Model files (HTTPS/TLS 1.2+)
    MM->>OV: loadModel()
    OV-->>MM: Model ready

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 4: HuggingFace Model Pull
    MM->>HF: GET /api/models/{repo}<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN Bearer
    HF-->>MM: Repository metadata
    MM->>HF: git clone via libgit2<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    HF-->>MM: Model repo + LFS objects
    MM->>OV: loadModel()
    OV-->>MM: Model ready
